    "asOf": "2019-06-27",
    "date": "2022-04-19T16:29:58Z",
    "text": "Dollar-for-Dollar Deficit Reduction Act\n\nThe bill establishes a framework to require legislation that increases or suspends the public debt limit to include spending reductions that are equal to or greater than the projected increase in debt that will occur under the legislation. The bill allows the spending reductions to be phased in over a 10-year period."
